{"TopicId":205175,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Did i encountered a new kraken?","CreatedByName":"Pod4898","CreatedById":216522,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-07T15:08:37Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Pod4898","CreatedById":216522,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-07T15:08:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. Today i made a spaceplane that looked very fine to me. One flaw it had was due to the annoying kraken made it spin sideways. Even using \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E or even \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E doesn\u0027t fix the sideway-spinning kraken. Even restarting multiple times doesn\u0027t fix the annoying kraken.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nedit: I realized it was that tiny little annoying dragging \u003Cspan\u003E@ssh0le basically why does even atmospheric drags exist?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-10-18T11:00:29Z\u0022 title=\u002210/18/2021 11:00  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 18, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Pod4898\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steuben","CreatedById":77368,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-07T15:10:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably not.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny pics of the plane?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pod4898","CreatedById":216522,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-08T10:55:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nok i\u0027ll try\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-08T16:19:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224040792\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022205175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221633619317\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216522\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pod4898\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/7/2021 at 4:08 PM, Pod4898 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. Today i made a spaceplane that looked very fine to me. One flaw it had was due to the annoying kraken made it spin sideways. Even using \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E or even \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E doesn\u0027t fix the sideway-spinning kraken. Even restarting multiple times doesn\u0027t fix the annoying kraken.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably because you designed it asymmetrically or messed up a setting on one of the ailerons. Have you also tried doing Alt\u002BX? That\u0027ll reset your trimming.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pod4898","CreatedById":216522,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-09T07:24:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk so, here\u0027s my spaceplane.\u00A0\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/Iyobwn7\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/a/Iyobwn7\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Echo__3","CreatedById":204997,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-09T10:24:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour plane has no yaw control. Try adding a vertical stabilizer and rudder.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pod4898","CreatedById":216522,"CreatedDa